hopobject.body: We're at university together ursodiol drugs.com 'Romantic’ is the same word Weber uses to describe the work of his mentor, Diane Arbus, whose probing images of dwarfs, giants and circus performers always provoke strong emotions in viewers. He says, 'When I think about Diane’s photo of the little boy with the hand grenade in Central Park, it reminds me of myself. You know, not having too many friends, and trying anything to get attention.’
